Text: One of the best, thank you

Works great but if you want to use the advanced filesystem editor (to move the MFT, pagefile, etc) this does not work, I do not recommend trying either as after trying and failing with this one then installing UD3 from their website and doing the same thing it corrupted my hard drive and I had to reinstall Windows.
BUT if this is not what you use UD3 for then this download is 100% perfect.
